strong>Jessica</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaO10c780i_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggaO10c780i_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/Review_3_1.png?v=1776655768"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvhyMnth1O_text","label":"ggvhyMnth1O_text","default":"<p>\"I've got sensitive skin and I've tried every Korean mask on TikTok. Most of them break me out or leave my skin red. This one didn't sting, didn't irritate, and by morning my skin looked plumper than it has in years. Finally one that works AND doesn't punish my face.\"</p><p><br>★★★★★ (5/5) — <strong>Stephanie</strong></p>"}],
